<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-python_track_AEA">
<p>
For this course we use the following resources:
</p>

<ul class="org-ul">
<li>Jean Tirole, <a href="https://press.princeton.edu/titles/10919.html">Economics for the Common Good</a>,</li>
<li>for students following the python track in this course: We are very happy that we partner with <a href="https://www.datacamp.com/">datacamp</a> for this course to teach you python. <a href="https://www.datacamp.com/about">Datacamp</a> offers great on-line courses for you to learn python.</li>
</ul>

